			<Properties>
				<ProtectedString name="Source"><![CDATA[--[[

	Welcome to Void-Sentinel [Beta v0.1]!

	Setup:
	1. Place the "Void-Sentinel" folder inside ServerScriptService.
	2. Configure the anticheat in the "Settings" module script.

	Optional:
	- You may delete this README script.

	Customization:
	- You are allowed to modify the anticheat for personal use.
	- Rebranding or republishing it as your own project is not allowed.

	Important:
	- Void-Sentinel is still in active development.
	- Bugs and false positives may happen.

--]]]]></ProtectedString>
